{
  "texts": [
    "This involved identifying whether a stroke was a forehand clear, a backhand drive, or altogether not a stroke.",
    "We annotated the beginning and end of each stroke in real-time, using Unix time, while also recording the type of each stroke.",
    "To annotate each participant's skill level, we recruited three professional badminton coaches.",
    "Each coach had an average of 18 years of professional training and playing experience, with over 7 years of coaching experience (Age: Mean = 36.7, SD = 11.3; Years of Educational Experience: Mean = 18, SD = 2.6; Years of Coaching Experience: Mean = 8.2, SD = 1.3).",
    "These coaches were assigned the task of observing participants' videos and rating their forehand clears and backhand drives on a scale ranging from 1 to 7."
  ]
}